<br>
848 X 480    should be /viewport 0 0 769 420<br>
1024 X 768  should be /viewport 0 0 928 672<br>
1152 X 964  should be /viewport 0 0 1044 844<br>
<br>
etc etc<br>
<br>
basically, the first number of your videa resolution and multiply it by 90.6%  and multiply the second number by 87.5%... That will get you the exact size of your viewport as Lion shows in his screenshot, regardless of your video resolution.<br>
