<br>
ie.  if you have your screen resolution set to 1024x768, and you want your playable area to be 800x600, subtract 800 from 1024 to get the x number to use.  So using those numbers to put the playable area to right and have black portion on left use /viewport 224 0 800 600  that will give you black on bottom and left.  if you want to move it down, subtract height of the playable area from screen height and use that for y position.  Again using the same numbers above /viewport 224 168 800 600  would give you a playable area lower right with black on top and left. <p><p><center><A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=168780" target=_blank><b>Xaranik Draggonsfist</b></a><br>
