<br>
to move &quot;center&quot; the window<br>
<br>
0 0 is top left<br>
1024 0 is top right<br>
0 768 is bottom left<br>
1024 768 is bottom right<br>
<br>
so to shift down and to the left<br>
/viewport 30 30 900 600<br>
would put a 30 pixel wide stip along the top and left sides <p>Brother Lenardo Draconis<br>
